node.text: We are honored to be the first residential real estate brokerage to earn the WELL Health-Safety Rating from the International WELL Building Institute (@WellCertified), a leading organization focused on advancing health and wellbeing in buildings globally. The WELL Health-Safety seal means an enhanced wellness experience for our clients, agents, staff, and office guests. Proud to join great organizations including @Yankees, @EmpireStateBldg, @TMobile and @JPMorgan in creating a world focused on health and well-being.

node.title: The Agency Earns WELL Health-Safety Seal

40288 Pine Bench Road • Offered at $6,950,000 • 5 beds, 9 baths • Listed by @mumansky18, @safia.lasman & @karenmorrisproperties. Link in bio for all the details.

node.text:
The 825 Croft at Melrose Place is a brand new, modern residential offering located in the heart of West Hollywood, blocks from the world-famous Melrose Place. The collection of 15 exquisitely crafted residences features 2 and 3 bedroom floor plans, private balconies, Wolf appliances, Quartz countertops, Nest thermostats and White Oak floors. Residents enjoy a private rooftop deck for gathering, relaxing and entertaining amidst panoramic city and Hollywood Hills views.

825 N. Croft Avenue • Offered from $1,399,000 - $1,899,000 • 2 and 3 bedroom residences available • Listed by @lapropertiesbyazy. Link in bio for all the details.
